Australian broadcaster SBS has sacked its football reporter Scott McIntyre over his ` inappropriate and disrespectful ' ANZAC day tweets .
McIntyre condemned the commemoration of ANzacAC Day on Twitter , calling it ` the cultification of an imperialist invasion , and accusing Australian Diggers of committing war crimes ` widespread rape and theft .
McIntyr 's comments referred to the Anzac 's landing on the Gallipoli Peninsula in Turkey .